@Robin: I work on Walls and Nebula (if you talk about gamemode section) 

@Nath: I actually quite like the "Emerald" rank. It shows that I helped Avicus by donating $50 to help with it's progress.

@Loo: I'm in 9th

@Frosted: I just came back from school and it was great. First day of High school ;)

@Mapdev:  Color: Red | Sport: Soccer/Football | Fav Genere: Any

@Zac: How do you "c" someone? I can see you though. I can see your profile pic which is your irl picture but how do you "C" someone?

@Wandom: A favorite map I made is Maisosen. My favorite map overall, (IS NOT 50 SHADES) is Planks.

@Spookeh: Favprite moment was when I didn't talk for 10 minutes during the Final Match in TOC and I got the monument and everyone in the Teamspeak chat was like "WTF HAPPENED"

@DaFrozen: I love the Assassin's Creed series and I play some Pokemon games when I'm bored.

@Raging: no I can't even :c Watch: 2, 4, 5 GAHHHH. How do I even?

@Dent: 17 years (I'll fix it sometime this week)

@Smiley: To hang out with my friends and be happy. I smiled 120% today!!!!
